&lt;p>with the Cividis version:&lt;/p>
&lt;p>&lt;img src="https://tdj28.github.io/p/using-pnnls-new-cividis-colormap-in-data-science-to-make-accessible-heat-maps/assets/Cividis-heatmap-69d2bb6c.png"
width="1482"
